This program is a fork of Petter Säterskogs MandarinTrainer. It is used to learn facts as fast as possible. It
contains a small but easily extendible database of facts. The program is also made to collect and display
statistics on the learning. This can be used to improve the program.

This program is written by Petter Säterskog, petter.saterskog@gmail.com. See COPYING for license information.